body: This is the "Happy end" sequel of #390276. Labelled 1, so maybe more to come. Just hope it's not a bait-and-switch. After his childhood friend, and her mother, and his sister are made into sex slave by an Elite. In this one, he managed to become an elite himself and make his revenge. He got that old man arrested and publicly humiliated. The girls now serve him, but he already lost faith on girls too, seeing how easily they betrayed him, yet now they're licking his feet. The author also have a version where he got gender bent and made into sex slave (#394456), so there could be other endings too coming up.
